<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tailwindcss/browser@4"></script>
</head>
<body>


   <div class="w-full min-h-screen bg-zinc-900 text-white p-10">

    <section class="bg-zinc-800 p-6 rounded-md mb-8">
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">About This Project</h2>
        <p>This is a backend project built using <strong>Express.js</strong> with <strong>MongoDB</strong> integration.</p>
        <p>The application uses <strong>MongoDB</strong> as the server-side database and is deployed globally on <strong>Render</strong>.</p>
      </section>

    <h3 class="text-3xl mb-5">Create Account</h3>
    <a href="/about" class="text-sm text-blue-400 hover:underline">About This Project</a>

    <form action = "/register" method="post">
        <input class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md outline-none bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="text" placeholder="name" name="name">
        <input class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md outline-none bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="age" placeholder="age" name="age">
        <input class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md outline-none bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="number" placeholder="number" name="number">
        <input class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md outline-none bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="email" placeholder="email" name="email">
        <input class="px-3 py-2 rounded-md outline-none bg-transparent border-2 border-zinc-800" type="password" placeholder="password" name="password">
        <input class="px-5 py-2 rounded-md bg-blue-500" type="submit" value="Create Account">
    </form>
    <p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-400">
        Already have an account?
        <a href="/login" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">Login</a>
      </p>

      <footer style="text-align: center; margin-top: 50px; color: #777;">
        &copy; 2025C All rights reserved
      </footer>

   </div>
</body>
</html>